+1 useful application for the military 📲 Legal organization "Princip" has launched a mobile application for military personnel, veterans and their families. It has several important functions at once:

- catalog of places of social services: medical facilities, social services, contacts and work schedule, as well as information on how to get there;
- important notifications: updates in the procedures that apply specifically to you (this will help you learn about important changes in time, including payments). You can download the application here⬇Google play:https://bit.ly/49HA8jxAppStore:https://apple.co /42OwKkL
